Messages.Value: Good morning, thank you for calling the travel agency. My name is Lucas Thompson, how can I assist you today?
Yes, I'm having trouble with a recent booking I made with your agency. My name is Sarah Jones and I had a flight and hotel reservation to Los Angeles last week.
I'm sorry to hear that, Sarah. Can you please provide me with your reservation number so I can take a look at your booking?
Sure, it's 123ABC and my departure city was Chicago.
Thank you for that information, Sarah. Can you please tell me what specific issue you experienced during your travels to Los Angeles?
Yes, my flight was delayed for several hours and when I arrived at the hotel, they did not have any record of my reservation. I had to spend the night in the lobby before they found a room for me.

I apologize for the inconvenience, Sarah. I will need to log a ticket for this and escalate it to our support team who will investigate the issue and provide a resolution to you. Can you confirm the best phone number and email address to reach you at?
Yes, my phone number is 555-123-4567 and my email is sarahjones@email.com.
Thank you, Sarah. I will log a ticket immediately and follow up with you as soon as I have more information on the issue.
